### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get all students
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students

### Get one student
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/1

### Create student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_no": "2024004",
  "first_name": "Ali",
  "last_name": "Demir",
  "email": "ali@example.com",
  "department": "Software Engineering"
}

### Invalid student validation test
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_no": "2024005",
  "first_name": "Bad",
  "last_name": "Input",
  "email": "bad-email",
  "department": ""
}

### Partial update
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alex.new@example.com"
}

### Search by department
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/department/Software%20Engineering

### Add course to student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students/1/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course_code": "SWE401",
  "course_name": "Graduation Project"
}

### Get student's courses
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/1/courses

### Delete student
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/students/3
